{
  "chapter": 42,
  "chapter_summary": "项少龙与滕翼在韩境雪地伏击嚣魏牟追兵。二人利用陷阱和火攻，歼灭近百敌人大半，嚣魏牟肩中弩箭负伤欲逃。滕翼徒手拽住马腿将其拉下马，项少龙击杀征勒后，滕翼亲手将嚣魏殴击毙于拳下，割首级祭奠妻儿。项少龙从嚣魏牟身上找回飞虹剑。滕翼丧家后誓死追随项少龙。三人途经一边境村落，滕翼备受尊敬，结识精擅追踪的年轻猎人荆俊，荆俊恳求追随项少龙外出闯荡。四人参加当地婚礼习俗，荆俊探知魏赵边防严密，找到隐秘水道，趁大雪夜色掩护安然回到赵境。",
  "dialogues": [
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "speaker_name": "项少龙",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "滕兄是否自小便在这里狩猎维生？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 42,
      "line_start": 6,
      "line_end": 6
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_teng_yi",
      "speaker_name": "滕翼",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "实不相瞒，我本有志于为我韩国尽点力量，所以曾加入军伍，还积功升至将领，后来见上面的人太不像样，只知排挤人才，对外则摇尾乞怜，心灰意冷下带着家人，隐居于此，岂知……",
      "tone": "沉声",
      "chapter": 42,
      "line_start": 8,
      "line_end": 8
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "speaker_name": "项少龙",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "至少有六、七十人！",
      "tone": "惊讶",
      "chapter": 42,
      "line_start": 14,
      "line_end": 14
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_teng_yi",
      "speaker_name": "滕翼",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "是九十至一百人。",
      "tone": "淡然",
      "chapter": 42,
      "line_start": 16,
      "line_end": 16
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "speaker_name": "项少龙",
      "listener": "char_teng_yi",
      "text": "你的观察很准确。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 42,
      "line_start": 18,
      "line_end": 18
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_teng_yi",
      "speaker_name": "滕翼",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "项兄你还是走吧！凭我们两人之力，加上陷阱也对付不了这么多人。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 42,
      "line_start": 22,
      "line_end": 22
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "speaker_name": "项少龙",
      "listener": "char_teng_yi",
      "text": "滕兄不要这么快便泄气，只要我们能坚持一会儿，天色一黑，将大利于我们的行动，哼！我项少龙岂是临阵退缩的人。",
      "tone": "沉声",
      "chapter": 42,
      "line_start": 26,
      "line_end": 28
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "speaker_name": "项少龙",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "是嚣魏牟！",
      "tone": "惊讶",
      "chapter": 42,
      "line_start": 32,
      "line_end": 32
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_teng_yi",
      "speaker_name": "滕翼",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "是齐国的嚣魏牟！",
      "tone": "惊讶",
      "chapter": 42,
      "line_start": 34,
      "line_end": 34
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_teng_yi",
      "speaker_name": "滕翼",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "项兄不要自责，这完全不关你的事，你亦是受害者罢了！",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 42,
      "line_start": 34,
      "line_end": 36
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_wei_mu",
      "speaker_name": "嚣魏牟",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "我绝不会错的，项少龙诈作朝楚国逃去，只是掩眼法。而他若要回赵，仅有三条路线，谅他也不敢取道我们的大齐和魏国，剩下只有这条韩境的通道，但为何仍找不到他呢？",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 42,
      "line_start": 46,
      "line_end": 49
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zheng_le",
      "speaker_name": "征勒",
      "listener": "char_xiao_wei_mu",
      "text": "我们是乘船来的，走的又是官道，比他快十来天也不出奇，现在我们布置停当，只要他经过这里，定逃不过我们设下的数十个岗哨。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 42,
      "line_start": 52,
      "line_end": 53
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_wei_mu",
      "speaker_name": "嚣魏牟",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "记得不可伤赵倩！",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 42,
      "line_start": 56,
      "line_end": 56
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zheng_le",
      "speaker_name": "征勒",
      "listener": "char_xiao_wei_mu",
      "text": "头子！那间屋……",
      "tone": "焦急",
      "chapter": 42,
      "line_start": 60,
      "line_end": 60
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_wei_mu",
      "speaker_name": "嚣魏牟",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "这么精彩的东西，再看一次也是好的，我最爱看被我奸杀的女人。",
      "tone": "冷笑",
      "chapter": 42,
      "line_start": 62,
      "line_end": 63
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "speaker_name": "项少龙",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "嚣魏牟逃哩！",
      "tone": "激动",
      "chapter": 42,
      "line_start": 100,
      "line_end": 100
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "speaker_name": "项少龙",
      "listener": "char_teng_yi",
      "text": "滕翼！追！",
      "tone": "激动",
      "chapter": 42,
      "line_start": 110,
      "line_end": 110
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "speaker_name": "项少龙",
      "listener": "char_teng_yi",
      "text": "滕兄今后有何打算？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 42,
      "line_start": 144,
      "line_end": 144
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_teng_yi",
      "speaker_name": "滕翼",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "我什么都没有了，除一人一剑外，再无挂虑。项兄若不嫌弃，以后我滕翼便跟随你，什么危难艰险也不会害怕，直至被人杀死，好了结这凄惨的命运！",
      "tone": "沉声",
      "chapter": 42,
      "line_start": 146,
      "line_end": 149
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "speaker_name": "项少龙",
      "listener": "char_teng_yi",
      "text": "我喜欢还来不及，但滕兄不须如此郁结难解，不若振起意志，重过新的生活吧！",
      "tone": "欣喜",
      "chapter": 42,
      "line_start": 152,
      "line_end": 153
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_teng_yi",
      "speaker_name": "滕翼",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "项兄不会明白我对妻儿和亲人的感情，那是我生命的一切，现在我已一无所有，除了项兄的恩德外，我再不会对任何人动感情，那太痛苦了。",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 42,
      "line_start": 156,
      "line_end": 157
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_teng_yi",
      "speaker_name": "滕翼",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "唉！爱哭的小公主！",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 42,
      "line_start": 162,
      "line_end": 162
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "speaker_name": "项少龙",
      "listener": "char_teng_yi",
      "text": "嚣魏牟的首级很有价值，滕兄有没有方法把它保存下来？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 42,
      "line_start": 164,
      "line_end": 165
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_teng_yi",
      "speaker_name": "滕翼",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "这个容易得很，包在我身上好了！",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 42,
      "line_start": 168,
      "line_end": 168
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_jing_jun",
      "speaker_name": "荆俊",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "滕大哥！",
      "tone": "激动",
      "chapter": 42,
      "line_start": 184,
      "line_end": 184
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhao_qian",
      "speaker_name": "赵倩",
      "listener": "char_jing_jun",
      "text": "小心点啊！不要摇晃了！",
      "tone": "担心",
      "chapter": 42,
      "line_start": 188,
      "line_end": 188
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "speaker_name": "项少龙",
      "listener": "char_jing_jun",
      "text": "朋友好身手。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 42,
      "line_start": 196,
      "line_end": 196
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_teng_yi",
      "speaker_name": "滕翼",
      "listener": "char_jing_jun",
      "text": "荆俊还不下来！",
      "tone": "厉声",
      "chapter": 42,
      "line_start": 198,
      "line_end": 198
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_jing_jun",
      "speaker_name": "荆俊",
      "listener": "char_zhao_qian",
      "text": "这位气质高贵的美丽小姐，请问有了夫家没有？",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 42,
      "line_start": 200,
      "line_end": 201
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_teng_yi",
      "speaker_name": "滕翼",
      "listener": "char_jing_jun",
      "text": "修修你那张没有遮拦的油嘴吧！这位是赵国金枝玉叶的三公主，怎轮到你无礼？",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 42,
      "line_start": 206,
      "line_end": 207
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_jing_jun",
      "speaker_name": "荆俊",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "这位定是大破灰胡和人狼的项少龙了！",
      "tone": "激动",
      "chapter": 42,
      "line_start": 210,
      "line_end": 211
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_teng_yi",
      "speaker_name": "滕翼",
      "listener": "char_jing_jun",
      "text": "你怎晓得？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 42,
      "line_start": 214,
      "line_end": 214
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_jing_jun",
      "speaker_name": "荆俊",
      "listener": "char_teng_yi",
      "text": "听边境的魏兵说的，并嘱我替他们留心项爷和公主的行踪，若有发现，会给我一百个铜钱。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 42,
      "line_start": 216,
      "line_end": 217
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhao_qian",
      "speaker_name": "赵倩",
      "listener": "char_jing_jun",
      "text": "你不会那么做吧？",
      "tone": "恐惧",
      "chapter": 42,
      "line_start": 220,
      "line_end": 220
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_jing_jun",
      "speaker_name": "荆俊",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "当然不会，在下还立下决心追随项爷，到外面闯闯世界，项爷请答应小子的要求。",
      "tone": "恳求",
      "chapter": 42,
      "line_start": 222,
      "line_end": 223
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_teng_yi",
      "speaker_name": "滕翼",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "荆俊是这里最优秀的猎人，精擅追踪和偷鸡摸狗之道。今天我特别到这个村子来，是想项兄见见这终日梦想要到外面见识闯荡的小子。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 42,
      "line_start": 228,
      "line_end": 231
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "speaker_name": "项少龙",
      "listener": "char_jing_jun",
      "text": "起来吧！以后跟我好了！",
      "tone": "豪迈",
      "chapter": 42,
      "line_start": 234,
      "line_end": 234
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_jing_jun",
      "speaker_name": "荆俊",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "让小子先去探路，明早必有报告！",
      "tone": "欣喜",
      "chapter": 42,
      "line_start": 236,
      "line_end": 237
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_teng_yi",
      "speaker_name": "滕翼",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "今晚假若听到异响，切莫出来，因为会有人来偷村长的女儿。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 42,
      "line_start": 242,
      "line_end": 243
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_teng_yi",
      "speaker_name": "滕翼",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "是本地的风俗，婚礼的前一晚举行偷新娘的仪式，大家装作若无其事，新郎偷了姑娘回家后，立即洞房，明早天亮前回到娘家举行婚礼，你们可顺便喝杯喜酒。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 42,
      "line_start": 248,
      "line_end": 249
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhao_qian",
      "speaker_name": "赵倩",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "项郎啊！倩儿也要那样穿起新娘喜服嫁给你。",
      "tone": "温柔",
      "chapter": 42,
      "line_start": 258,
      "line_end": 259
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "speaker_name": "项少龙",
      "listener": "char_zhao_qian",
      "text": "有朝一日逃出邯郸，我们立即学他们般举行婚礼好吗？",
      "tone": "温柔",
      "chapter": 42,
      "line_start": 262,
      "line_end": 263
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_jing_jun",
      "speaker_name": "荆俊",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "魏、赵间的边防比平时严密了很多，人人摩拳擦掌要拿项爷和公主去领赏，幸好我知道有条隐秘的水道，若趁大雪和夜色掩护，定可偷往赵国去。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 42,
      "line_start": 272,
      "line_end": 273
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "speaker_name": "项少龙",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "希望快点下雪就好了！",
      "tone": "欣喜",
      "chapter": 42,
      "line_start": 276,
      "line_end": 276
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_teng_yi",
      "speaker_name": "滕翼",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "今晚必有一场大雪。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 42,
      "line_start": 278,
      "line_end": 278
    }
  ],
